OL,5, The BBC says it has been in touch with 
OL,6, police following claims one of its     
OL,7, presenters paid a teenager #35,000 for 
OL,8, sexually explicit photos.              
OL,10,FThe corporation says it is working as  
OL,11,Fquickly as possible to establish the   
OL,12,Ffacts and that the presenter, who it   
OL,13,Fhas not named, has been suspended.     
OL,15,FClaims the presenter began paying the  
OL,16,Fyoung person when they were 17 were    
OL,17,Ffirst reported by the Sun on Friday.   
OL,19,FPolice said the BBC was in contact but 
OL,20,Fno formal allegation has yet been made.
